==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Carboy
<hw>Car"boy</hw> <pr>(k⟦aum⟧r"boi)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Cf. Ir. &
Gael <ets>carb</ets> basket; or Pers <ets>qur⟦amac⟧bah</ets> a sort of
bottle.]</ety> <def>A large, globular glass bottle, esp. one of green
glass, inclosed in basket work or in a box, for protection; -- used
commonly for carrying corrosive liquids; as sulphuric acid,
etc.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

